# S05-T06: Epics Right-Column UI

## Objective
Make the proposed epics fully user-owned (invariant §2).

## Execution
- Right-column component lists `wc_epics` for the active chat with the lead-role badge
  (icon/color from `useAgentRoles()`, T02).
- Per-epic actions: rename, edit summary, delete, change lead role; column action: create.
  Each mutation is a REST write + optimistic update + `epic.updated` broadcast (T09).
- "Drag back to chat" → drops the epic title/summary into the prompt as a re-ask seed.
- Prominent per-epic **Accept** button (wired in T07). Glass UI = `card-glass-*` (S04 §9).

## Out
`apps/work-control/app/components/EpicsColumn.vue` + epic REST routes/composable

## Done when
- All five manipulations work and persist; role badge reflects taxonomy.
